{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1707-08_319","head":{"value":"Epitalame sur le mariage de Monsieur le Duc d’Estrées, avec Mademoiselle de Nevers","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", août 1707 [tome 8], p. 319-325.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"La varieté estant toûjours de saison, &amp; tres-agreable dans un ouvrage, j’ay crû devoir separer l’Article des Nouvelles d’Allemagne que vous venez de lire, d’avec celuy de l’Epitalame qui suit. Je ne vous dis point le nom de son Auteur, quoy qu’il soit tres-connu, &amp; qu’il ait fait des ouvrages d’un grand éclat, &amp; qui ont esté fort applaudis du Public. Vous le sçaurez peut estre d’ailleurs ; mais j’ay crû que je vous le devois taire.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"EPITALAME","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"Sur le mariage de Monsieur le Duc d’Estrées, avec Mademoiselle de Nevers.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Himen, hâtez vous de descendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Venez unir deux illustres amans,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Songez qu’ils content les momens,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Repondez sans les faire attendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À leurs tendres empressemens.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour combler leurs desirs vous estes necessaires,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais en les unissant il faudroit vous deffaire,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un deffaut qui vous est reproché chaque jour,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Accordez vous avec l’Amour,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans le cœur des époux vous ne le souffrez guere,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec vous il faut d’ordinaire,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’attendre à ce fâcheux retour.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour ces nouveaux époux devenez plus aimable.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des nœuds qu’ils vont former ne soyez point jaloux,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Hymen, ce n’est pas trop de l’amour &amp; de vous ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour leur faire une bonheur durable.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la froideur ni le dégout,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les tristes soucis qui se glissent par tout,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que l’importun chagrin avec ses noires ailes,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les aigreurs ni les querelles,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne suivent point icy vos pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On vous trouveroit sans apas,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourquoy souffrir à vostre suite,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces sombres enfans du Cocite ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne nous amenez point ces hostes dangereux,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui troublent les Ris &amp; les Jeux,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui leur font prendre la fuite.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous pouvez aux mortels faire un sort assez doux,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Commencez par ces deux époux :","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne laissez marcher sur vos traces,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les Plaisirs avec les Graces,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lorsque vous le voulez vous avez des attraits ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Venez avec l’aimable Paix,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Amenez l’humeur sans caprice,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’elle ait de sages enjouemens,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la douceur avec elle s’unisse,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Joignez y tous les agrémens,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’esprit &amp; des sentimens,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La bonté, la delicatesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[12]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’égalité, la politesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[12]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[13]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et n’oubliez pas le devoir,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[13]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[14]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est luy dont le divin pouvoir,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[14]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De toutes les vertus fait éclater l’usage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[15]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est luy qui les fait naistre, elles sont son ouvrage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[16]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et c’est au devoir seul que les Dieux immortels,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[17]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[18]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Doivent ici bas leurs autels.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[18]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Faites que ces amans ne songent qu’à se plaire,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que leur union soit sincere,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de leur mutuelle ardeur,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nul soupir dérobé ne puisse les distraire,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qu’aucune flamme étrangere,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne surprenne jamais leur cœur.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Faites que toujours leur tendresse,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Se reveille par le desir,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’un même trait toujours les blesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’aucun bien ne puisse s’offrir,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou l’un sans l’autre s’interesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que dans tous les deux l’attrait du plaisir naisse,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’usage de leur plaisir.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin, je vous les recommande,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Himen, n’oubliez rien pour contenter leurs vœux,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est une entreprise assez grande,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De rendre deux époux heureux.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}